e following third parties:\n\nService providers: companies that deliver payment processing, hosting, analytics, technical support, and other services required to operate the Application.\n\nGovernment authorities: when required by law.\n\n4.2. We require all third parties with access to personal data to maintain confidentiality and ensure adequate protection.\n\n5. Data Security\n\n5.1. We implement organizational and technical measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.\n\n5.2. We use modern encryption and protection methods, including SSL/TLS for data transmission and encrypted password storage.\n\n6. User Rights\n\n6.1. You have the right to:\n\nAccess your personal data.\n\nUpdate your personal data.\n\nWithdraw consent for processing (when processing is consent-based).\n\nDelete your personal data.\n\nReceive information about how your data is processed.\n\nSubmit complaints to the authorized data protection authority.\n\n6.2. To exercise your rights, please contact us at: nullscode@yandex.kz.\n\n7. Contact Information\n\nContact person: Konstantin Galin\n\nEmail: nullscode@yandex.kz\n\nTelegram channel: https://t.me/nullscode\n\nPersonal Telegram: https://t.me/nolowcode\n\n8. Changes to the Policy\n\n8.1. We may update this Policy from time to time. The new version becomes effective once published in the Application.';

